2.text: Rusiru, his mother and an old lady are at the bus stop. Rusiru: Mother, the bus is here. Let's get in.
2.ssml: <speak><prosody rate='slow'><phoneme alphabet='ipa' ph='rusiru'>Rusiru</phoneme>, his mother and an old lady are at the bus stop. <phoneme alphabet='ipa' ph='rusiru'>Rusiru</phoneme>: Mother, the bus is here. Let's get in.</prosody></speak>

3.text: Mother: Rusiru, can't you see, there's an old lady behind you. Let her get on to the bus first.
3.ssml: <speak><prosody rate='slow'>Mother: <phoneme alphabet='ipa' ph='rusiru'>Rusiru</phoneme>, can't you see, there's an old lady behind you. Let her get on to the bus first.</prosody></speak>

5.text: Rusiru: I'm sorry, I didn't see you.
5.ssml: <speak><prosody rate='slow'><phoneme alphabet='ipa' ph='rusiru'>Rusiru</phoneme>: I'm sorry, I didn't see you.</prosody></speak>

7.text: The bus conductor: Hurry up, hurry up. Get in quickly. It's getting late.
7.ssml: <speak><prosody rate='slow'>The bus conductor: Hurry up, hurry up. Get in quickly. It's getting late.</prosody></speak>

8.text: Mother: Please wait, I have another big bag that I need to take with me.
8.ssml: <speak><prosody rate='slow'>Mother: Please wait, I have another big bag that I need to take with me.</prosody></speak>

9.text: The bus conductor: Can I help you with the bag?
9.ssml: <speak><prosody rate='slow'>The bus conductor: Can I help you with the bag?</prosody></speak>

10.text: Mother: Yes, thank you very much.
10.ssml: <speak><prosody rate='slow'>Mother: Yes, thank you very much.</prosody></speak>
